Quick usage guide
-----------------

  1. Get the ShellTools archive from the Fish disk 673, or from Aminet,
     @{b}util/cli/hacks204.lha@{ub}.

  2. Install the commands in this archive in your Shell search path,
     preferably C:.

  3. Put the command @{b}Set _pchar |@{ub} in your @{b}S:Shell-Startup@{ub} file.

  4. Restart your AmigaShell so that it reads the @{b}S:Shell-Startup@{ub}.

  5. Try @{b}List SYS: | More@{ub}

  6. Read the ShellTools documentation and experiment.


@EndNode

